

Many people in Davis play with flying discs, most commonly known by the brand specific frisbee.  From casual games of toss at local parks, possibly with dogs a canine companion, to serious sports like ultimate Frisbee and Frisbee golf, there are opportunities for all levels and interests of players.  If youre a students student at UCD, you might consider the UC Davis Womens Frisbee Team or UC Davis Mens Frisbee Team, both part of the UCD Intramural Sports & Sport Clubs.  Campus also has the UCD Frisbee Golf Course.
